<plot>BEACHBOUND is a story about redemption. Margie, 13, takes the first steps away from childhood and into the exciting new world of teenagers with a fab new bikini, but isn't sure how far she wants to go. Her father recognizes her struggle. He lets her know that it's all right--she'll be accepted, and loved, by him, even as she's starting to leave her childhood behind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?061930</url></doc>
